name: Minids
tagline: C library implementing basic data structures like stacks, queues, binary search trees, etc.
body:
Minids
======

C shared library implementing common data structures like stacks, queues, hash tables etc.

Latest release and source tarball can be obtained from

https://github.com/asterix17n/Minids/releases

Minids Github Page

http://asterix17n.github.io/Minids/

Minids Facebook Page

https://www.facebook.com/pages/Minids/427191397406905


ï»¿Building & Installing Minids
==============================

To build and install Minids type the following commands
   
    ./configure
    ./make
    ./make install
